---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Anabolic Therapies Research" description="Research on injections that stimulate tissue healing">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-stone-900 text-white py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <a href="/research" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-400 hover:text-white text-sm mb-6 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
          </svg>
          Back to Research Library
        </a>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 rounded-full">
            Research in Progress
          </span>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="font-display text-display-md md:text-display-lg text-white mb-4">
          Anabolic Therapies & Injections
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
          The broad field of anabolic injections focuses on stimulating injured tissues to healâ€”accelerating 
          healing, shutting down inflammation, limiting scar formation, and recruiting the body's self-repair cells.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="font-display text-display-sm text-stone-900 mb-6">
          Research Currently Underway
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Our anabolic therapies research program is actively investigating new biologic solutions 
          for tissue healing. Published findings will be added to this library as studies are completed.
        </p>
        
        <div class="divider divider--center mb-8"></div>
        
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-stone-800 mb-4">Areas of Investigation</h3>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-left mt-8">
          <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 rounded-sm">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-stone-900 mb-2">Platelet-Rich Plasma (PRP)</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
              Concentrated growth factors from the patient's own blood to accelerate tissue repair.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 rounded-sm">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-stone-900 mb-2">Hyaluronic Acid</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
              Joint lubrication and anti-inflammatory effects for cartilage preservation.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 rounded-sm">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-stone-900 mb-2">Growth Factor Injections</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
              Targeted delivery of healing signals to injured tissues.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 rounded-sm">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-stone-900 mb-2">Combined Protocols</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
              Optimizing timing and combination of anabolic agents for maximum effect.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-purple-50 border-t border-purple-100 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Support This Research</h3>
      <p class="text-stone-600 mb-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Help us develop new biologic solutions for people who want to stay active after injury or arthritis.
      </p>
      <a href="/donate" class="btn-primary inline-flex">
        Donate to SRF
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
